#     7-MAY-1999 (MBT):
#        Generated IFD file from IFL file.
#     20-JUL-2000 (MBT):
#        Rewrote to accommodate change from IDI to Tcl GUI.
#     9-APR-2001 (MBT):
#        Upgraded for use with Sets.
#     19-JUL-2001 (MBT):
